     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="13"/>
   <head>THE AVTHOR.</head>
   <l>I Would not feare with <hi>Cinick</hi> Doggs to fight</l>
   <l>Came they in <hi>Front</hi>: But, this will ill be borne;</l>
   <l>Perhaps some Curres behind my Backe will bite:</l>
   <l>But that's their <hi>shame,</hi> my <hi>glory</hi> it to scorne.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>ROVVLAND VAVGHAN.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
